# Cursor Execution Harness (Frontend)

**Scope:** [`CLAUDE.md`](CLAUDE.md) · **Vault:** `docs/Frontend/` only (Backend vault와 wikilink 분리).

> [`REACT_RULES.md`](REACT_RULES.md) is mandatory for UI work.

---

## Before `frontend/` changes

1. Repository root `CLAUDE.md` — blueprint + agent behavior
2. [`CLAUDE.md`](CLAUDE.md) — layout, API integration
3. [`REACT_RULES.md`](REACT_RULES.md) — React patterns (full rules)

API 도메인 계약: code tree `backend/apps/{app}/_docs/CLAUDE.md` (vault wikilink 없음).

---

## Quick rules

| Item | Rule |
|------|------|
| Routes | `app/**/page.tsx` |
| API helpers | `lib/*-api.ts` |
| State | One object per related UI state — avoid field-per-`useState` |
| Forms | `FormData`; capture `form = e.currentTarget` before `await` |
| Errors | Inline UI — no `alert()` |
| Backend HTTP | `http://127.0.0.1:8000`; Titanic `/titanic/*` |

---

